港人意願<br />\n為賺錢 英國出賣香港<br />\n<br />\n英方又指絕大部份港人都是華人，對英國無感情聯繫，故不擬討論港人自決前途權利，更明言「不會堅持談判結果一定要與港人意願一致（nor insist that any solution must be in line with their wishes）」，談判目標是與中國達成協議，令香港繼續繁榮，讓英國有機會賺錢（Our aim is an agreement with China under which the territory continues to prosper in a way that provides opportunities for Britain to make money）。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140205/18615623\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140205%2F18615623&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=81e87fc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140205%2F18615623&h=ab38eb7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140205/18615623</a><br />\n<br />\n簽《聲明》當日早上<br />\n鐵娘子趙紫陽密斟大亞灣核電合約<br />\n<br />\n新一批解密文件中，有一封外相賀維私人秘書里基茨的信件，透露賀維與戴卓爾夫人曾考慮帶同包括GEC的商界成員訪京，但諮詢港督尤德後擔心會被香港傳媒大肆報道，造成「我們將香港賣給中國後，現在收到獎品（getting our prize for having sold out Hong Kong to the Chinese）」的印象而打消念頭。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20141231/18986739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20141231%2F18986739&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=104af095\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20141231%2F18986739&h=d117e1b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20141231/18986739</a>"},{"pid":"f77fb42f9e476e9676661135fc8bf8bc408140d9","tid":1820760,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:45:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c52ee5ffbc6a1f91d69ae852625a604fdd97e0d9","tid":1820760,"uid":5502,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:48:50.000Z","msg":"可以唔使再對